snippet.title: Air Guitar Warrior for Kinect - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Step inside the game and become a legendary Air Guitar Warrior with the power of Kinect! Play air guitar and control the music in this blend of music game and arcade action. Includes 19 custom-made tracks from Mr. Fastfinger and Samppa Siurala. Out now on Xbox One
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/air-guitar-warrior-for-kinect/bw1v96v2x5xb
How to play Air Guitar - WARRIOR STYLE: https://youtu.be/DMuXFJegN9Y
Soundtrack preview: https://youtu.be/xbhJRHKA7C8
http://airguitarwarrior.com
